These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: milk, tea, sprite, almond-milk
Sport: lacrosse, handball, basketball, baseball
1. Beverage:milk is on the right of Sport:basketball##1
2. Sport:baseball is on the far left##1
3. Sport:basketball is between Sport:handball and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:sprite is between Beverage:tea and Beverage:milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | tea   | sprite | milk       |
| Sport      | baseball | lacrosse | basketball   | handball |

