Nationality: brazilian, thai, nigerian, chinese
1. Nationality:chinese is between Hobby:fishing and Nationality:thai##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is on the right of Nationality:brazilian##1
4. Hobby:sudoku is on the left of Nationality:brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | sudoku | fishing | woodworking |
| Nationality   | thai    | chinese   | brazilian | nigerian       |

