2. Nationality:malaysian is between Nationality:american and Food:strawberry##2
3. Nationality:american is on the far left##1
4. Nationality:italian is on the left of Food:avocado##1
5. Food:strawberry == Nationality:italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | broccoli    | eggplant | strawberry   | avocado  |
| Nationality   | american | malaysian   | italian | japanese |

